      "content": "---\ntype: Race\nraceCategory: Humanoid\nplayable: true\nsize: Medium\naffinity:\n  - Water\n  - Spirit\nvisibility: public\ntags:\n  - Race\n  - aquatic\n  - riverfolk\n  - water-touched\n---\n\n# Undien\n\nThe Undien are water-touched people adapted to rivers, coasts, deep lakes, and ancient drowned ruins.\n\n## Traits\n\n- Amphibious affinity\n- Water movement familiarity\n- Strong connection to aquatic cultures\n\n## Racial Skills\n\n- River Navigation\n- Breath Control\n- Drowned Ruin Lore\n\n## Character Forge Notes\n\nUndien are available as a playable race. They are best suited to campaigns with rivers, coastlines, drowned ruins, spirit-touched waters, or maritime cultures.\n\n## Test Note\n\nThis is a clean test race page used to verify the public compendium system.\n",
